420
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:52,520
<font color="#ffff00">Intanto</font>
<font color="#ffff00">stilo il referto del tuo paziente.</font>

421
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,880
<font color="#ffff00">Grazie, arrivederci.</font>

422
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,920
<font color="#ffff00">A dopo, professore.</font>

423
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:05,960
<font color="#ffff00">Non ha la narcolessia e</font>
